visibility: SANDBOX
license: OFL
category: handwriting
subsets: menu,latin

family: Rouge Script

designer: TypeSenses

approved: true
description: <p>Rouge Script is a formal \
  script type, initiall drawn by hand \
  with a copperplate nib and redrawn \
  with the termination style of a brush \
  script. This gives it the flavor of a \
  casual script.</p> \
  <p>It is very soft and has fast curves, \
  while its low slant angle makes it very \
  legible and improves the render on-screen. \
  It works perfectly for titles or short \
  phrases in branding, magazines, food, \
  feminine and fashion related typography.</p>

font.RougeScript-Regular.ttf.style: normal
font.RougeScript-Regular.ttf.weight: 400

